00:04:40.113 --> 00:04:41.364
{\an8}Baiklah.

00:04:41.447 --> 00:04:44.284
Rupa-rupanya, pesakit
berkata buruk tentang Patrick,

00:04:44.367 --> 00:04:45.827
sebab tu Kai naik marah.

00:04:47.912 --> 00:04:49.289
Puan Olivia.

00:04:50.873 --> 00:04:53.626
Saya sudah bercakap dengan Cik Zelda.
